19:07.639 --> 19:09.872
I'm sorry your birthday's been such a bust.

19:11.743 --> 19:13.877
I really tried to get someone to hit you.

19:13.878 --> 19:16.446
It's all right.

19:16.447 --> 19:18.282
It's just nice to know you care.

19:18.283 --> 19:20.984
But I do have one last birthday surprise

19:20.985 --> 19:22.718
that unexpectedly arrived.

19:23.721 --> 19:25.254
I think you're going to love it.

19:26.958 --> 19:30.093
How would you like an unprovoked war

19:30.094 --> 19:31.727
with the kingdom of Hortensia?

19:33.464 --> 19:35.065
Best birthday present ever.

19:35.066 --> 19:37.366
[Both laugh]

19:39.137 --> 19:41.171
Dingdong.

19:41.172 --> 19:44.173
♪

19:44.609 --> 19:46.175
[Chuckles]

19:48.313 --> 19:49.613
Nice throw, son.

19:49.614 --> 19:51.014
Thanks, dad.

19:51.015 --> 19:53.150
This cabbage is spent.

19:53.151 --> 19:54.950
I'll grab another.

19:55.420 --> 19:57.287
- Stop!
- Finish him!

19:57.288 --> 19:59.589
- Get the king!
- Cheaters! Ch...

19:59.590 --> 20:01.925
[children laughing]

20:01.926 --> 20:04.026
Ow! Galavant!

20:05.330 --> 20:07.630
Sid! You escaped!

20:09.334 --> 20:11.468
[Chuckles]

20:11.469 --> 20:13.670
All right, okay. That's... that's close.

20:13.671 --> 20:14.471
Too close.

20:14.472 --> 20:15.706
Okay.

20:15.707 --> 20:17.407
Oh, it's good to see you, sir.

20:17.408 --> 20:19.142
I have news.

20:19.143 --> 20:20.911
Princess Isabella is being forced to marry

20:20.912 --> 20:21.978
her cousin in Hortensia.

20:21.979 --> 20:25.082
I know. And I'm not gonna let it happen.

20:25.083 --> 20:26.883
I'm gonna raise an army to rescue her.

20:26.884 --> 20:28.819
Then I've got something you'll want.

20:28.820 --> 20:30.387
Look out!

20:30.388 --> 20:32.222
Wild monkeys!

20:32.223 --> 20:33.357
Your sword!

20:33.358 --> 20:34.558
Raar!

20:34.559 --> 20:35.592
[Grunts]

20:35.593 --> 20:37.727
Roberta: Richard, they're children!

20:39.230 --> 20:41.263
Galavant, look out!

20:41.966 --> 20:43.233
[Fleshy thud]

20:43.234 --> 20:44.233
[Gasps]

20:45.837 --> 20:48.105
[Gasps]

20:48.106 --> 20:50.272
No-o-o!

20:53.010 --> 20:54.978
Oh, what have I done?

20:54.979 --> 20:58.113
I've had worse.

21:00.098 --> 21:02.098
Maybe not.

